snippet.title: Death Road to Canada: Hot Dog Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Death Road to Canada is out RIGHT NOW on Steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/252610

Take a randomly generated road trip to Canada! Try to manage a car full of jerks in an upbeat and weird Zombie apocalypse. Up to 500 slow zombies can track you down at the same time.

Features interactive fiction group management with random character personalities and stats that give you different options each time you play. Death Road to Canada has a big focus on strange, rare events. Recruit superintelligent dogs that stand on their hind legs, sumo wrestlers, armored knights, and more!

http://www.deathroadtocanada.com
